snippet.title: Top 10 Parody Songs HATED by the Original Artist
snippet.description:
Not everyone can take a joke... Join us as we count down our picks for the parody songs that seriously upset the original artists! Our countdown includes "Amish Paradise," "Gay Fish," "Couch Potato" and more! From Weird Al making Coolio furious to SNL making Taylor Swift send apology flowers, these musical spoofs struck a nerve with their inspiration. Whether it was Eminem blocking Weird Al's video, Paul McCartney cringing at The Rutles, or Garth Brooks confronting Cledus T. Judd in a parking lot over Grammy concerns, these artists didn't appreciate becoming the punchline. Which parody do you think crossed the line? Let us know in the comments below!
